05:52.800 --> 05:54.960
I feel kind of like I'm committing a crime.

05:54.960 --> 05:58.640
And that's what $1,250 looks like.

05:59.280 --> 06:04.560
There's this kind of sadness that sets in as they realize that the $2,000 pizza

06:04.560 --> 06:09.280
isn't worth it at all, and they start to feel almost like they've done something immoral.

06:09.280 --> 06:13.120
It's a feeling I've had many times myself after spending too much money

06:13.120 --> 06:17.680
on some gilded piece of trash in a vain attempt to fill the hollow in my soul.

06:17.680 --> 06:19.520
Is there a name for that feeling?

06:19.520 --> 06:23.040
Well, I like to call it fucking neoliberalism.

06:23.040 --> 06:26.320
