07:21.680 --> 07:24.320
So it's not like those shitty YouTube comments that go

07:24.320 --> 07:28.080
PIZZAS IN AFRICA COULD HAVE EATEN THOSE CHILDREN HOW DARE YOU

07:28.080 --> 07:31.520
