07:31.520 --> 07:34.960
for buying inexpensive flatbread smeared with gilded cream cheese.

07:34.960 --> 07:39.120
The problem is our economy fundamentally operates in a way that makes inevitable

07:39.120 --> 07:42.640
these repulsive juxtapositions of scarcity and abundance.

07:42.640 --> 07:45.760
