08:54.080 --> 08:58.640
Of course, some capitalists are terrible people, but some probably aren't.

08:58.640 --> 09:02.880
And either way, the virtues or vices of the rich are sort of beside the point.

09:02.880 --> 09:06.480
So the real point of the golden pizza is that it's emblematic of the fact

09:06.480 --> 09:11.600
that the extreme economic inequalities of our society are laughably unjustifiable.

09:11.600 --> 09:14.880
If I were to translate the meaning of the golden pizza into an argument,

09:14.880 --> 09:16.560
